            "notes": "This deck focuses on generating tokens with Slimefoot, the Stowaway, and sacrificing them for value with cards like Goblin Bombardment. Squee, Goblin Nabob provides a consistent source of creatures to sac for various effects. The deck also includes a variety of efficient removal spells and disruption to control the board while building its own army of saprolings. The goal is to overwhelm the opponent with a swarm of creatures, draining their life total with Slimefoot's ability or finishing them off with direct damage from cards like Lightning Bolt. The deck aims to be aggressive and proactive, putting pressure on the opponent from the early turns of the game."
