            "notes": "The deck focuses on utilizing Slimefoot and Squee as strong aggro commanders to overwhelm opponents with a combination of efficient creatures, removal spells, and powerful synergies. By utilizing cards like Elves of Deep Shadow, Llanowar Elves, and Birds of Paradise to ramp up quickly, the deck aims to establish a threatening board presence early on. The inclusion of cards like Goblin Bombardment and Phyrexian Tower enables sacrificing creatures for additional value, while cards like Birthing Pod and Eldritch Evolution provide toolbox options to fetch key creatures. With a mix of creature aggression, sacrifice synergies, and efficient removal, the deck aims to chip away at opponents' life totals while maintaining a strong board presence."
